g.text: For a dog owner, you can
browse availability of dog sitters for your dates and price range on a map/list
can view available dog sitter’s profiles, (name, approximate location, # of past sits, etc.)
can see all the upcoming reservations and the “sits” your dog has been on
set what time ranges you can sit via an “availability calendar”
can see all the upcoming reservations and “sits” that you’ve completed
Create booking in the bookings table
Delete availability of the sitter in the availbility table
Use DB as the global lock
if two people delete availbility at the same time
then the second person will be thrown an eerror
at the database level and asked to rebook from the clientt
